<br>
Anyway, what I am asking for here is just a quick review of what I have now, and a few suggestions of what I should get to help out.  My monk is level 14 now, probably 15 by the end of the day.  I'm hanging out in Kurn's Tower for the moment.  One thing to note, is that I also have a steel ulak, but I've been using my Bo primarily.  <br>
<br>
Thanks in advance!<br>
<br>
Heer<br>
14th Level Monk on Tribunal<br>
<br>
