<br>
Chest: Crystal Covered Shroud 100pp or so<br>
A lot less weight and more AC<br>
<br>
Neck: Ulthork Hide 10-50pp<br>
30hp, 7AC. Nice, underrated neck piece.<br>
<br>
Ear: Orc Fang Earrings 20-50pp each<br>
30hp for the pair<br>
<br>
Head: Lumberjack's Cap 25-75pp<br>
10ac if I recall correctly... weighs less than what you have on... <br>
<br>
The rest, fill in with Wu's, which druid can make, and Spore Covered, which is insanely cheap, and you should be set!<br>
<br>
As for weapons, get a Fighting Baton or Cane of Tranquil to train up 1hb in your main hand.<br>
<br>
