<br>
A couple more suggestions: Try to find something to replace the Straw Spun Belt. At 6.0 wt, that is really going to hurt you in a few levels when you want to loot or carry anything at all. (Like your Bo stick to practice 2hb) I recommend Spider Fur. They've dropped to around 200pp now, but if that's too far out of your ballpark (granted that will last you quite some time... the next best upgrades from that cost a fortune) then just pick up a Wu's or Cured Silk Sash. You'll lose a few AC, but you would've lost it anyway from the Straw Spun and the penalty it will put you at.<br>
<br>
Pants, you may want to trade for Wu's. Higher AC, lower wt, and agi. Those are the only two things I see causing any major trouble for you in the future.<br>
<br>
Fighting Baton has a slightly better ratio, but it's only .04 of a difference, so I would stick with the CoT.<br>
