<br>
I wear the Robe of Living Fungus over the Crystal Covered Shroud (I think the +sta outweighs the 2ac difference, but I have a Crystal Covered Shroud in the bank for cold resist).  If you can find it cheap it would be a nice change of color (There are a lot of monk twinks wearing Crystal Covered Shrouds, and not all that many wearing Robes of Living Fungus, which has a green look that in my opinion looks great on an Iksar).  <br>
<br>
My 6ac 65hp rings (~400p each) have made me last longer in a fight, and would have a larger effect on a low level monk.<br>
<br>
Orc Fang Earrings are a nice, cheap start.  A more pricy alternative would be Black Sapphire Electrum Earrings.<br>
<br>
Good weapons will help you do much more damage, but its benefit is not as great when grouped.  Those which you have are a nice start.<br>
<br>
Black Panther is decent armor.  So is Acrylia Reinforced.<br>
<br>
Azure sleeves, at 12ac, is a great arm item for monks. <p>-Korph
